## Svelte 5 Runes Quick Reference

- `$state(value)` - Reactive state
- `$derived(expr)` - Computed values
- `$effect(() => {})` - Side effects (avoid for state sync)
- `$props()` - Component inputs
- `$bindable()` - Two-way bindable props
